overview.en: Cell chain (CELL) is a value-based circulation application based on blockchain technology. It provides a number of stem cell commercial applications for users in the global stem cell field, and creates a health management industry application with decentralization and high security and asset preservation and appreciation. Platform, and through the series of product applications to achieve efficient and convenient daily health management and voting decisions, so that each group of users with cell chain integrates investors, decision makers, consumers and promoters, directly facing the world's best and Complete stem cell medical, rehabilitation, and health management services.
overview.zh: 细胞链（CELL）是基于区块链技术的价值流通应用，它为全球干细胞领域内用户，提供多项干细胞商业应用，打造具备去中心化和高度保障性以及资产保值升值特征 的健康管理产业应用平台，并通过系列产品应用实现高效、便捷的日常健康管理与投票决策，使每个拥有细胞链的群体用户集投资者、决策者、消费者以及推广者于 一身，直接面对全球最为优秀和完善的干细胞医疗、康复、健康管理服务。
